12:41.281 --> 12:43.347
what's at issue here. You are here today

12:43.348 --> 12:45.685
because you lied to her.

12:45.686 --> 12:46.955
Up, bup, bup, bup, bup, bup, bup!

12:46.956 --> 12:49.224
<i>Webster's Dictionary,</i>

12:49.225 --> 12:51.192
which I'm sure you're familiar with...

12:51.193 --> 12:53.896
I'm sure all these good
people, familiar with it...

12:53.897 --> 12:57.868
