as a falsehood, an untruth.

12:57.869 --> 13:00.403
All I did was kind of alter plans.

13:00.404 --> 13:04.774
- No lies were uttered.
- Thank you for the vocabulary lesson, Mr. Greenberg.

13:04.775 --> 13:06.675
What about when you said... and I quote...

13:06.676 --> 13:08.677
