13:47.168 --> 13:49.234
"Uh, reservation? What reservation?"

13:49.235 --> 13:52.269
(laughs) So creepy. Yeah... yeah. So scary.

13:52.270 --> 13:54.607
- Remember how gross that pool was?
- Oh, my God.

13:54.608 --> 13:57.008
