- Oh.

14:14.368 --> 14:16.000
Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't... (stammers)

14:16.001 --> 14:17.568
Are friends not allowed
to touch each other's hands?

14:17.569 --> 14:19.137
I didn't realize that.

14:19.138 --> 14:21.673
Of course they are. Wh-What's next?

14:21.674 --> 14:24.472
No more high fives? A ban on
fist bumps, perhaps, eh?

14:24.473 --> 14:27.076
(laughter) All right. What about the wine?

14:27.077 --> 14:28.245
- Explain that.
- Aha!

14:28.246 --> 14:30.547
<i>Webster's Dictionary</i>

14:30.548 --> 14:34.714
defines wine as "the fermented
juice of grapes used especially

14:34.715 --> 14:37.820
- as a bev..." I'm sorry. 
- I didn't mean explain wine.

14:37.821 --> 14:40.423
We know what wine is. (groans)

14:40.424 --> 14:42.125
There's a precedent
for grown-ups sharing a bottle

14:42.126 --> 14:43.561
- of wine at dinner.
- Oh, really?

14:43.562 --> 14:44.962
- Mm-hmm.
- But when's the last time

14:44.963 --> 14:46.729
that you and Mike shared a bottle of wine?

14:46.730 --> 14:50.201
Shared a bottle of wine
and touched each other's hands?

14:50.202 --> 14:52.803
Listen, we-we can... we
can jibber-jabber all day,

14:52.804 --> 14:54.537
back and forth Jibber-jabber a second time.

14:54.538 --> 14:56.841
Until we're as... mixed up as a-a...

14:56.842 --> 14:58.810
three-legged horse at a rodeo.

14:58.811 --> 15:01.646
(woman chuckles, man coughs)

15:01.647 --> 15:02.647
One lady.

15:02.648 --> 15:04.115
Thank you, ma'am.

15:04.116 --> 15:06.720
Uh, but the-the fact remains,

15:06.721 --> 15:09.024
I have done nothing wrong.

15:09.025 --> 15:10.960
(sighs) Goddamn it.

15:10.961 --> 15:13.296
All right, my hands are tied.

15:13.297 --> 15:14.898
Due to a lack of hard evidence,

15:14.899 --> 15:17.368
this court is forced to rule
in Josh's favor.

15:17.369 --> 15:19.703
No one high-five him.

15:19.704 --> 15:21.504
- Thank you. She did.
- JUDGE: Oh...

15:21.505 --> 15:22.438
(annoyed): Susan...

15:22.439 --> 15:24.477
(yawning)

15:24.478 --> 15:26.146
- Hey.
- Oh.

15:26.147 --> 15:28.182
I am so tired.

15:28.183 --> 15:30.084
Yeah.

15:30.085 --> 15:32.516
Oh. Yeah, I guess... I guess it's late.

15:32.517 --> 15:34.017
It is late.

15:34.018 --> 15:35.754
I should probably go.

15:39.290 --> 15:41.526
Or-or-or...

15:41.527 --> 15:44.695
or... we-we, uh...

15:44.696 --> 15:47.198
could watch something.

15:47.199 --> 15:48.665
Like what?

15:48.666 --> 15:51.268
We never finished <i> Carnivàle.</i>

15:51.269 --> 15:52.068
(gavel banging)

15:52.069 --> 15:53.904
I know, I know.

15:53.905 --> 15:56.241
People watch shows together
