16:03.247 --> 16:05.549
A-a date? Specifically a date?

16:05.550 --> 16:06.817
- Yes.
- Because...

16:06.818 --> 16:08.084
the dictionary might disagree.

16:08.085 --> 16:09.017
(Groaning) Oh, God, the dictionary...!

16:09.018 --> 16:11.252
Oh, fuck you off.

16:11.253 --> 16:14.927
<i>Webster's</i> defines a date
as a romantic outing, okay?

16:14.928 --> 16:17.796
- So did we go... did we go out?
- No. No. No.

16:17.797 --> 16:20.032
