The point is what I'm trying to say is

16:43.467 --> 16:47.068
technically...
I haven't done anything wrong.

16:47.069 --> 16:49.304
- Well, technically, no, you haven't.
- Aha!

16:49.305 --> 16:50.740
Technically, no, I haven't.

16:50.741 --> 16:52.041
You said technically I
haven't done anything wrong.

16:52.042 --> 16:54.443
That means... that means I win.

16:56.678 --> 16:59.845
Remember this day.

16:59.846 --> 17:02.778
The day that blind Lady Justice

17:02.779 --> 17:04.547
took her own life.

17:06.016 --> 17:07.717
It is with great shame

17:07.718 --> 17:10.484
and utter disgust...

17:10.486 --> 17:13.623
that this court is forced
to rule in Josh's favor.

17:13.624 --> 17:15.558
Thanks, man.

17:15.559 --> 17:17.060
"Thanks, man"?

17:17.060 --> 17:19.060
Don't type that. What are...

17:19.061 --> 17:21.394
Goddamn it.

17:21.395 --> 17:23.866
MAN: The moment you put on that
red nose and threw in your lot

17:23.867 --> 17:25.635
